ey_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maye-E Wong/REUTERS  MANILA, Philippines - Filipina boxer Aira Villegas is setting her sights on a more ambitious goal after ending her Paris Games run with abronze medal.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9993851382893133, \"rank\": 0.0005932201353713561, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9119026888188293, \"rank\": 0.09660823473174592, \"text\": \"Filipina\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}, {\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aira\", \"score\": 0.9999887417811175, \"rank\": 6.211500996216435e-06, \"text\": \"Aira\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aira\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villegas said her next target is an Olympic gold as she took her loss to Turkey's Buse Naz Cakiroglu in the women's 50kg semifinals at the Roland Garros Stadium in stride.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9989662482001027, \"rank\": 0.001034040132811376, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To my younger self, I know that you are already proud of me.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And to my future self, I will make you even prouder,\\\" Villegas said in a mix of Filipino and English during an interview with Olympic broadcaster Cignal.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\", \"score\": 0.9333440881000722, \"rank\": 0.07141028560336321, \"text\": \"Cignal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cignal_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will do everything to accomplish my dreams of having our national anthem played for me in the Olympics before I retire.\\\"\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Villegas lost via unanimous decision as Cakiroglu - a former world champion and a Tokyo Games silver medalist - flexed her might, with her crisp and powerful punches meriting a standing eight count in the opening round.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The scores at the end were 30-26, 30-26, 30-27, 30-27, 30-27.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the defeat denied her of a chance to fight for the gold, the pride of Tacloban City said she simply lost to a deserving winner.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tacloban\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tacloban City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tacloban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tacloban\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not super disappointed because I did my best.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She studied me and I have to admit that she's really a good boxer,\\\" said Villegas.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sorry to the Filipinos who stayed up late to watch me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\"